    <item>
      <title>特朗普有罪判决为 2024 年大选增添转折：一名重罪犯被定罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/trump-guilty-verdict-adds-twist-to-2024-race-a-convicted-felon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普在曼哈顿刑事审判中被判有罪，这给陷入僵局的总统竞选注入了一个爆炸性且难以预测的新变量，主要特点是选民对他们选择两位知名且不受欢迎的主要候选人感到沮丧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/trump-guilty-verdict-adds-twist-to-2024-race-a-convicted-felon</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 23:18:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉法死亡人数不断增加，拜登坚持“走钢丝”的以色列政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/biden-sticks-to-tightrope-israel-policy-as-rafah-deaths-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数月来，拜登总统的顾问一直向国内外盟友坚称，他对以色列的支持遏制了总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡的冲动，并防止了更严重的流血事件，从而为加沙战争带来了最不坏的结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/biden-sticks-to-tightrope-israel-policy-as-rafah-deaths-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国高级官员称人工智能内容交易面临反垄断关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/ai-content-deals-face-antitrust-spotlight-top-justice-department-official-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部最高反垄断官员乔纳森·坎特 (Jonathan Kanter) 表示，美国司法部正在密切监视 OpenAI 等人工智能公司与内容创作者达成的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/ai-content-deals-face-antitrust-spotlight-top-justice-department-official-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 22:39:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>威利斯称新西兰预算对新西兰央行来说是朋友而非敌人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/willis-says-new-zealand-budget-is-friend-not-foe-to-rbnz</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰财政部长尼古拉威利斯坚称，她的首份预算不会让利率长期维持在高位，尽管经济学家警告称，这可能会使央行抑制通胀的努力变得复杂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/willis-says-new-zealand-budget-is-friend-not-foe-to-rbnz</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 22:06:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中美国防部长在新加坡寻求的不只是握手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/us-china-military-chiefs-seek-more-than-empty-handshake-at-shangri-la-dialogue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，在新加坡举行的年度防务会议上，中美两国军方领导人在晚宴前仅仅握手。这一次，他们的目标更高，但幅度不大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/us-china-military-chiefs-seek-more-than-empty-handshake-at-shangri-la-dialogue</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在封口费案中所有罪名成立。现在怎么办？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/trump-is-guilty-in-hush-money-case-what-happens-next</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普的刑事封口费审判的陪审团仅用了两天时间就做出了历史性的判决：34 项罪名全部成立。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/trump-is-guilty-in-hush-money-case-what-happens-next</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 21:54:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以下是导致特朗普有罪判决的关键审判时刻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/here-are-the-key-trump-trial-moments-that-led-to-guilty-verdict</link>
      <description><![CDATA[判定唐纳德·特朗普伪造商业记录的陪审团在做出这一历史性判决之前，已经收到了近五周的大量证词和证据，但有几个关键时刻脱颖而出，可能对曼哈顿审判期间的陪审团产生了影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/here-are-the-key-trump-trial-moments-that-led-to-guilty-verdict</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 21:53:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普竞选团队在判决有罪后发出捐款呼吁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/trump-uses-criminal-conviction-to-spur-donations-from-supporters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 试图将自己的犯罪定罪变成金子，呼吁捐助者为他陷入困境的总统竞选活动捐款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/trump-uses-criminal-conviction-to-spur-donations-from-supporters</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 21:51:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>唐纳德·特朗普成为首位被判有罪的美国前总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/trump-jury-says-it-has-reached-a-verdict-in-hush-money-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这是美国历史上第一起针对前总统的刑事审判，唐纳德·特朗普被判有罪，这一判决可能会在选举日五个月前重塑政治格局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/trump-jury-says-it-has-reached-a-verdict-in-hush-money-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 20:39:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
